WEBVTT

00:00:02.345 --> 00:00:03.865
- Shit!
- I don't even know

00:00:03.945 --> 00:00:05.105
if I'll be the next corpse!

00:00:05.185 --> 00:00:07.145
Did Bell and Cherreen have
any problems with each other?

00:00:07.225 --> 00:00:09.265
Cherreen was the only one
who had a key card to Bell's room.

00:00:09.345 --> 00:00:12.505
Someone must have received a letter
and hasn't told us yet.

00:00:12.585 --> 00:00:14.585
And that person could be Tonkla.

00:00:15.705 --> 00:00:16.825
Hey!

00:00:17.425 --> 00:00:18.305
Hello?

00:00:18.385 --> 00:00:24.665
Have you ever heard that
curiosity kills the cat?

00:00:24.745 --> 00:00:25.865
What do you mean by that?

00:00:25.945 --> 00:00:27.345
Hey!

00:00:28.545 --> 00:00:29.745
Jade!

00:00:54.785 --> 00:00:59.305
Do you like my welcome gift,

00:00:59.385 --> 00:01:01.385
Inspector Kamin?

00:01:54.345 --> 00:01:55.865
Do you know The Wild Hunt?

00:01:57.025 --> 00:02:00.345
This is where Jade got attacked
when he was investigating the case.

00:02:00.425 --> 00:02:02.705
This club is hardcore as hell.

00:02:02.785 --> 00:02:04.265
I've been there two or three times.

00:02:04.345 --> 00:02:09.225
It's where rich high-society types
come to do drugs.

00:02:14.305 --> 00:02:15.865
But I never did drugs.

00:02:18.305 --> 00:02:19.225
Good.

00:02:21.625 --> 00:02:23.785
So Jade was attacked
by people from The Wild Hunt?

00:02:29.345 --> 00:02:30.545
Yes.

00:02:37.465 --> 00:02:38.785
If you're worried,

00:02:38.865 --> 00:02:40.385
tell him when he comes to.

00:02:41.105 --> 00:02:42.185
No way.

00:02:42.825 --> 00:02:44.665
I'd rather bite my tongue and die.

00:02:47.785 --> 00:02:49.345
I'll go downstairs
to get something to eat.

00:02:59.185 --> 00:03:00.145
Kamin.

00:03:01.225 --> 00:03:02.465
Are you okay?

00:03:03.705 --> 00:03:05.065
Where does it hurt?

00:03:05.145 --> 00:03:06.385
It hurts.

00:03:15.625 --> 00:03:16.825
It hurts right here.

00:03:20.065 --> 00:03:22.545
If you still have the energy to talk back,

00:03:22.625 --> 00:03:23.905
you must be fine.

00:03:25.345 --> 00:03:26.945
I'm leaving.

00:03:27.025 --> 00:03:28.545
Hey!

00:03:28.625 --> 00:03:31.065
You're really going to leave
an injured person like this?

00:03:39.065 --> 00:03:40.145
Drama queen.

00:03:43.705 --> 00:03:45.825
Hey, stay with me.

00:03:47.945 --> 00:03:49.665
Stay with me, will you?

00:04:25.465 --> 00:04:28.305
This kiss means I'm worried.

00:04:30.145 --> 00:04:31.385
Just worried?

00:04:33.225 --> 00:04:37.105
I already told you yesterday
to take care of yourself.

00:04:37.185 --> 00:04:38.745
Look at you now.

00:04:41.185 --> 00:04:42.785
You're so strict, huh?

00:04:44.905 --> 00:04:46.305
Don't get hurt again, okay?

00:04:49.505 --> 00:04:51.305
When I say I'm worried,

00:04:53.105 --> 00:04:55.105
I don't say it to just anyone.

00:04:56.785 --> 00:04:58.265
And every time I say it,

00:04:59.985 --> 00:05:01.825
I really mean it.

00:05:05.065 --> 00:05:07.905
Seon Jae is moving faster
than we expected.

00:05:08.945 --> 00:05:11.905
He probably knows we're onto him.

00:05:13.225 --> 00:05:15.545
But Captain Jade was ambushed.

00:05:15.625 --> 00:05:16.705
We need to move fast.

00:05:16.785 --> 00:05:18.145
Seeing you this tense,

00:05:18.225 --> 00:05:21.025
I can't tell whether you're worried that
Seon Jae is ahead of us,

00:05:21.105 --> 00:05:22.825
or you're worried about Jade.

00:05:25.065 --> 00:05:27.345
I just don't want things
to end up like it did back then.

00:05:33.825 --> 00:05:36.545
This place isn't just about drugs.

00:05:36.625 --> 00:05:39.505
They also run illegal boxing matches.

00:05:39.585 --> 00:05:42.185
Any fighter who loses…

00:05:42.265 --> 00:05:44.345
When you find them again, they're dead.

00:05:44.425 --> 00:05:47.785
This time, the Special Investigation Unit
will lead the operation.

00:05:49.305 --> 00:05:50.625
And you're going in yourself?

00:05:50.705 --> 00:05:51.825
Not my team.

00:05:51.905 --> 00:05:54.985
The operation is led by Yu
from the Special Investigation Unit.

00:05:57.745 --> 00:05:59.265
Yu?

00:05:59.345 --> 00:06:02.825
I'm just curious
what a cop's daily life is like.

00:06:02.905 --> 00:06:03.785
Look at you.

00:06:03.865 --> 00:06:06.465
You're working all day, every day.
I've never seen you date anyone.

00:06:06.545 --> 00:06:08.465
But wait. What about Yu?

00:06:09.505 --> 00:06:10.345
Are you two dating?

00:06:17.265 --> 00:06:18.305
Yes.

00:06:18.385 --> 00:06:20.305
If you get information on
Lee Seon Jae of The Wild Hunt,

00:06:20.385 --> 00:06:21.745
please update me.

00:06:22.585 --> 00:06:24.145
Yes, Inspector.

00:06:26.785 --> 00:06:28.505
Damn it, Jay.

00:06:28.585 --> 00:06:31.025
I told you I could shower by myself.

00:06:31.665 --> 00:06:33.705
If I don't wipe you down,
you won't shower at all.

00:06:33.785 --> 00:06:35.785
- There are nurses, you know.
- You're filthy as hell.

00:06:35.865 --> 00:06:38.025
- You think I don't know that?
- Jay, have you eaten yet?

00:06:38.105 --> 00:06:39.585
Not yet.

00:06:40.385 --> 00:06:41.505
I'll take care of Jade then.

00:06:43.825 --> 00:06:45.425
Okay. I'll leave him to you.

00:06:58.545 --> 00:07:00.145
You know how to do this, right?

00:07:03.145 --> 00:07:04.425
Trust me.

00:07:08.785 --> 00:07:10.065
You can press harder.

00:07:11.785 --> 00:07:13.065
It doesn't hurt.

00:07:16.625 --> 00:07:18.625
The doctor said you can be discharged

00:07:19.225 --> 00:07:21.545
and go home in just two days.

00:07:21.625 --> 00:07:23.025
What?

00:07:23.105 --> 00:07:24.505
Two days?

00:07:25.385 --> 00:07:27.585
Honestly, I'm already fine.

00:07:27.665 --> 00:07:29.945
- I can even go home today.
- Hey, come on.

00:07:31.425 --> 00:07:33.265
I'm not done wiping you yet.

00:07:36.865 --> 00:07:38.825
All right then.

00:07:56.665 --> 00:08:00.425
So, how far have you gotten on Seon Jae?

00:08:00.505 --> 00:08:04.585
I'm tracking him down.

00:08:05.465 --> 00:08:07.025
But don't worry.

00:08:07.105 --> 00:08:09.705
I'll take care of every charge for you,

00:08:09.785 --> 00:08:13.825
including drugs or assaulting an officer.

00:08:16.025 --> 00:08:18.025
Can you handle it alone?

00:08:18.105 --> 00:08:19.625
Of course.

00:08:21.425 --> 00:08:23.025
If I weren't good enough,

00:08:23.945 --> 00:08:25.505
I wouldn't be an inspector.

00:08:26.665 --> 00:08:28.625
I'm not saying you're not good.

00:08:30.105 --> 00:08:31.945
I just want to work with you.

00:08:44.745 --> 00:08:46.585
Before we talk about the case,

00:08:47.665 --> 00:08:49.825
can we talk about us first?

00:08:52.505 --> 00:08:56.665
What exactly are we?

00:08:59.425 --> 00:09:01.585
I'm your superior.

00:09:01.665 --> 00:09:02.945
You're my subordinate.

00:09:03.025 --> 00:09:05.985
What kind of superior
kisses their subordinate?

00:09:06.705 --> 00:09:08.065
Tell me.

00:09:09.625 --> 00:09:11.465
Let's talk about this

00:09:11.545 --> 00:09:14.385
after the Seon Jae case is over, okay?

00:09:16.305 --> 00:09:18.025
If you don't feel anything,

00:09:18.105 --> 00:09:19.865
just tell me straight,

00:09:20.785 --> 00:09:22.745
so I know how to handle my feelings.

00:09:23.745 --> 00:09:25.065
Yeah.

00:09:36.865 --> 00:09:38.345
- Hey, Jay.
- Yeah?

00:09:38.425 --> 00:09:39.705
There'll be officers guarding you.

00:09:41.345 --> 00:09:43.185
No matter what,

00:09:43.265 --> 00:09:45.425
don't let anyone you don't know
come visit.

00:09:45.505 --> 00:09:47.385
- Understand?
- Understood.

00:10:07.065 --> 00:10:09.065
You already signed?

00:10:09.145 --> 00:10:11.385
Didn't you say three more days?

00:10:12.705 --> 00:10:13.865
Are you taking it or not?

00:10:13.945 --> 00:10:15.265
Of course I am.

00:10:18.025 --> 00:10:21.025
Then get some rest.

00:10:21.105 --> 00:10:22.665
All right. Goodbye.

00:10:23.185 --> 00:10:24.465
See you.

00:10:30.385 --> 00:10:31.785
Why the hell are you smiling?

00:10:32.865 --> 00:10:34.265
Latte.

00:10:38.825 --> 00:10:40.625
How did you know my usual is a latte?

00:10:43.705 --> 00:10:45.385
Kamin told me.

00:10:51.105 --> 00:10:52.625
Sweet, huh?

00:11:02.865 --> 00:11:04.545
Did you get called in too?

00:11:04.625 --> 00:11:05.945
Yeah.

00:11:07.145 --> 00:11:08.385
I was called in for questioning.

00:11:10.105 --> 00:11:14.185
Then why the hell are you here, Champ?

00:11:15.185 --> 00:11:16.545
I came to keep her company.

00:11:16.625 --> 00:11:18.065
She's scared.

00:11:21.585 --> 00:11:22.625
That smells like your perfume.

00:11:23.305 --> 00:11:25.025
Puifai just died.

00:11:25.105 --> 00:11:26.665
Did you two already sleep together?

00:11:26.745 --> 00:11:28.585
Stop running your mouth.

00:11:28.665 --> 00:11:30.185
It's because you're like this.

00:11:30.265 --> 00:11:33.865
Except for me, Fai, and Cher,

00:11:33.945 --> 00:11:35.665
no one wants you as a friend.

00:11:37.265 --> 00:11:39.585
Why do you always assume
the worst about me?

00:11:39.665 --> 00:11:43.825
Don't you remember
I'm the one who always helped you?

00:11:43.905 --> 00:11:46.545
Stop bringing up favors, asshole.
You're the worst piece of shit.

00:11:46.625 --> 00:11:48.105
You want me to say it?

00:11:48.665 --> 00:11:52.425
I'm sick of watching
you play the victim too.

00:11:53.505 --> 00:11:56.745
Hey, can we not make this worse?

00:11:59.705 --> 00:12:01.465
Just go back first, Champ.

00:12:01.545 --> 00:12:02.865
I'll let you know when it's done.

00:12:04.425 --> 00:12:06.025
This way, please.

00:12:06.105 --> 00:12:07.105
Go already.

00:12:33.265 --> 00:12:34.265
Hello.

00:12:34.345 --> 00:12:37.825
Lieutenant said you called
Tonkla and Cherreen in for questioning.

00:12:37.905 --> 00:12:38.905
I'll be right there soon.

00:12:38.985 --> 00:12:40.985
I told you to rest.

00:12:41.065 --> 00:12:42.865
What part of that is so hard
to understand?

00:12:42.945 --> 00:12:45.745
If I'm not there,
how are you going to pressure the kids?

00:12:46.345 --> 00:12:48.105
I've got solid evidence.

00:12:48.185 --> 00:12:51.945
This gang is covering up a secret
of their friends.

00:12:53.025 --> 00:12:54.905
But I don't know
if they're doing it out of love,

00:12:54.985 --> 00:12:56.465
or because they're involved themselves.

00:12:57.145 --> 00:13:00.905
Either way, we'll find out just
how much they love each other.

00:13:17.945 --> 00:13:21.105
What's your relationship with Tonkla?

00:13:21.705 --> 00:13:24.825
Well, we're just friends.

00:13:24.905 --> 00:13:26.265
But from what I see,

00:13:27.425 --> 00:13:31.985
the relationships between
Tonkla, Champ, and you are messy.

00:13:33.785 --> 00:13:35.585
Did Puifai know about this?

00:13:38.145 --> 00:13:41.025
Our friends have been dying one by one.

00:13:41.105 --> 00:13:43.345
Of course we're scared.

00:13:43.425 --> 00:13:45.225
Who knows who'll be next?

00:13:45.865 --> 00:13:47.465
I was just worried.

00:13:47.985 --> 00:13:49.145
I was afraid Cher might overthink things.

00:13:49.225 --> 00:13:50.625
You were worried about Cherreen?

00:13:50.705 --> 00:13:52.545
But Bell's death didn't matter?

00:13:54.145 --> 00:13:56.425
Is this what an unequal friendship
looks like?

00:13:56.505 --> 00:13:58.305
How the hell was I supposed to know

00:13:59.105 --> 00:14:00.785
Bell would actually die?

00:14:04.305 --> 00:14:05.785
You have a crush on Cherreen, don't you?

00:14:09.585 --> 00:14:11.025
How long has it been?

00:14:12.545 --> 00:14:14.345
He's the one trying on his own.

00:14:14.425 --> 00:14:16.305
I never led him on.

00:14:16.385 --> 00:14:19.425
Everyone in the group knows
we're just friends.

00:14:19.505 --> 00:14:22.705
But you benefit from him liking you.

00:14:23.545 --> 00:14:25.985
You can use him to survive.

00:14:27.225 --> 00:14:29.705
I have to stay in touch
with him as a friend

00:14:29.785 --> 00:14:32.905
because if I suddenly cut him off,

00:14:34.065 --> 00:14:36.185
he might completely lose it.

00:14:38.225 --> 00:14:39.825
And what about Champ?

00:14:46.785 --> 00:14:50.825
Which of your friends knows
you hooked up with him?

00:14:54.385 --> 00:14:55.905
This was even before Puifai died.

00:14:57.745 --> 00:14:59.745
Three people are dead now.

00:15:00.505 --> 00:15:03.705
Don't you ever think you could be next?

00:15:07.065 --> 00:15:10.345
Someone like you looks easy to pick on.

00:15:16.145 --> 00:15:18.385
I do feel guilty.

00:15:19.025 --> 00:15:22.985
But Champ threatened

00:15:23.065 --> 00:15:25.665
to kick me out of the group
if I didn't go along with it.

00:15:26.545 --> 00:15:29.785
You know how much influence he has.

00:15:33.785 --> 00:15:35.705
Even if you help her survive,

00:15:36.425 --> 00:15:38.065
she won't choose you.

00:15:40.025 --> 00:15:41.425
Just tell me already.

00:15:41.505 --> 00:15:43.865
What is your friend really like?

00:15:45.505 --> 00:15:47.185
- I don't know.
- Are you sure?

00:15:49.665 --> 00:15:51.905
- Do you know or not?
- I said I don't know, damn it!

00:16:08.465 --> 00:16:10.385
No one here is suspicious.

00:16:10.465 --> 00:16:11.865
We're all victims.

00:16:15.665 --> 00:16:16.585
What about this incident?

00:16:18.625 --> 00:16:20.385
Were you still victims?

00:16:21.345 --> 00:16:23.065
What the f*ck does this shit
have to do with anything?

00:16:26.665 --> 00:16:28.345
Whoever talks first survives.

00:16:29.265 --> 00:16:31.665
So why did you all
help to cover this case up?

00:16:38.305 --> 00:16:40.225
Cherreen has nothing to do with this.

00:16:41.185 --> 00:16:43.225
This is on me.

00:16:45.265 --> 00:16:46.985
But it's over already.

00:16:47.065 --> 00:16:48.825
Did you clear it?

00:16:50.225 --> 00:16:51.585
Or did Champ do it?

00:16:52.265 --> 00:16:53.745
Champ's not involved.

00:16:58.865 --> 00:17:00.585
If I'm going to prison,

00:17:00.665 --> 00:17:02.785
that bastard's going with me.

00:17:03.385 --> 00:17:05.665
He helped me get rid of
the body that night.

00:17:07.665 --> 00:17:09.464
Someone like him has no heart.

00:17:09.545 --> 00:17:10.985
He's playing two women at once.

00:17:11.665 --> 00:17:13.065
One of them died,

00:17:13.825 --> 00:17:15.385
and he doesn't feel a damn thing.

00:17:19.105 --> 00:17:22.585
If you're going to investigate us,
why don't you investigate Time instead?

00:17:23.704 --> 00:17:24.985
Cherreen.

00:17:26.265 --> 00:17:27.224
Time?

00:17:28.865 --> 00:17:30.545
What's so interesting about him?

00:17:34.425 --> 00:17:37.065
Tonkla accidentally hitting someone once

00:17:37.145 --> 00:17:39.305
doesn't even compare to the shit
Time does regularly.

00:17:40.185 --> 00:17:42.785
If you're going to arrest someone,
at least get the right guy.

00:17:43.825 --> 00:17:47.705
That bastard secretly
records himself having sex

00:17:47.785 --> 00:17:49.265
and sells the clips.

00:17:52.065 --> 00:17:53.625
He doesn't even spare
his own friends in the group.

00:17:55.665 --> 00:17:57.785
But his dad's a cop,

00:17:58.465 --> 00:18:00.305
so no one can touch him.

00:18:08.065 --> 00:18:09.745
Inspector, there's a letter.

00:18:32.945 --> 00:18:34.745
A dinner invitation?

00:18:36.025 --> 00:18:38.905
So tonight, you're really
walking straight into the lion's den,

00:18:38.985 --> 00:18:40.225
just like they invited you to?

00:18:42.105 --> 00:18:43.105
Yes.

00:18:43.905 --> 00:18:47.705
These people could be behind
the drug network tied to Tar.

00:18:48.385 --> 00:18:52.345
This might include the illegal drugs
injected into Puifai's body.

00:18:54.105 --> 00:18:58.825
Mirin said ordinary people
can't buy those drugs.

00:19:00.025 --> 00:19:03.785
But if we go in, we'll see who buys them.

00:19:04.305 --> 00:19:06.465
We might even hit the jackpot
and find the killer.

00:19:09.145 --> 00:19:10.305
How can you be so sure?

00:19:11.345 --> 00:19:12.865
Isn't this too risky?

00:19:14.825 --> 00:19:17.105
I've been watching Seon Jae
for a long time.

00:19:18.225 --> 00:19:21.625
You should focus on questioning the kids.

00:19:23.665 --> 00:19:25.145
Let me go with you.

00:19:27.665 --> 00:19:28.905
Hey.

00:19:29.865 --> 00:19:31.945
How long are you going to make me
worry about you?

00:19:32.705 --> 00:19:34.305
And have you ever thought that

00:19:35.065 --> 00:19:36.545
I worry about you too?

00:19:49.505 --> 00:19:50.865
Here you are.

00:19:54.825 --> 00:19:56.225
Your housewarming gift.

00:19:59.545 --> 00:20:01.145
Why a wolf?

00:20:02.185 --> 00:20:03.865
Isn't that your tattoo?

00:20:03.945 --> 00:20:07.225
Yeah. My tattoo.

00:20:07.825 --> 00:20:11.385
But wolves are arrogant, just like you.

00:20:12.345 --> 00:20:14.985
Though honestly,
you don't really suit a wolf either.

00:20:16.585 --> 00:20:18.145
You're too stubborn.

00:20:18.225 --> 00:20:19.985
You're more like a house dog.

00:20:22.225 --> 00:20:23.745
Yeah, I'm very stubborn,

00:20:25.145 --> 00:20:26.745
especially when it comes to you.

00:20:29.785 --> 00:20:31.105
Trust me.

00:20:32.185 --> 00:20:33.825
I do trust you.

00:20:34.585 --> 00:20:36.025
But no matter what,

00:20:37.145 --> 00:20:39.585
I won't let you face this alone.

00:20:41.785 --> 00:20:44.505
You'll always have me.

00:20:56.385 --> 00:20:58.025
What do you think Puifai's secret is?

00:21:03.265 --> 00:21:05.545
Maybe…

00:21:05.625 --> 00:21:08.865
Puifai is actually
the worst one in the group.

00:21:08.945 --> 00:21:10.865
Or maybe…

00:21:12.785 --> 00:21:14.825
she's just a pitiful victim.

00:21:15.345 --> 00:21:19.905
But I don't believe anyone
is 100 percent innocent.

00:21:22.265 --> 00:21:24.185
Everyone has secrets.

00:21:33.905 --> 00:21:35.665
I still haven't been able to accept it,

00:21:35.745 --> 00:21:37.905
so I haven't packed anything yet.

00:21:39.025 --> 00:21:42.905
Feel free to look around, officers.

00:21:42.985 --> 00:21:45.345
I'll wait downstairs.

00:21:45.425 --> 00:21:46.785
Thank you.

00:22:31.385 --> 00:22:32.225
Hey.

00:22:39.945 --> 00:22:42.225
{\an8}Having shitty friends is like
being alive in hell.

00:22:42.905 --> 00:22:44.625
{\an8}But why suffer alone?

00:22:45.265 --> 00:22:48.505
{\an8}Try dying and you'll see
their true colors.

00:22:49.225 --> 00:22:51.105
{\an8}Whether it's truth or dare,

00:22:51.705 --> 00:22:53.505
{\an8}they all have to die.

00:22:55.665 --> 00:22:57.745
That means Puifai was the first
to receive the letter.

00:22:59.265 --> 00:23:01.985
She was the beginning of everything.

00:23:02.065 --> 00:23:04.865
Suicide following the killer's invitation?

00:23:04.945 --> 00:23:06.865
But even if that's true,

00:23:08.385 --> 00:23:12.785
we still don't know who would want
Puifai and her friends dead.

00:23:13.465 --> 00:23:14.745
And we still don't know

00:23:16.825 --> 00:23:18.665
the exact order of the deaths.

00:23:25.425 --> 00:23:27.065
Ever since that day,

00:23:27.145 --> 00:23:29.505
I haven't gone into Fai's room.

00:23:29.585 --> 00:23:33.745
And I never knew anything
about the letter.

00:23:35.825 --> 00:23:37.705
Before all this happened,

00:23:37.785 --> 00:23:39.185
what was Puifai like?

00:23:39.265 --> 00:23:41.065
She was a good girl.

00:23:41.705 --> 00:23:43.145
Studious.

00:23:43.985 --> 00:23:46.665
Everyone said she was sweet.

00:23:47.185 --> 00:23:48.625
But lately,

00:23:49.945 --> 00:23:53.465
she became quiet.

00:23:53.545 --> 00:23:57.545
At first, I thought
she had a fight with Champ,

00:23:57.625 --> 00:24:00.145
or had problems at school

00:24:01.145 --> 00:24:02.705
until that day

00:24:03.465 --> 00:24:05.945
when she told me the truth.

00:24:17.425 --> 00:24:18.985
Fai was pregnant.

00:24:20.385 --> 00:24:21.785
Puifai was pregnant?

00:24:22.825 --> 00:24:24.145
Yes.

00:24:27.185 --> 00:24:32.705
Bell's Truth letter mentioned that
Bell took a friend to get an abortion.

00:24:33.945 --> 00:24:37.145
Which means the friend
who took Puifai for the abortion

00:24:37.225 --> 00:24:38.545
was Bell.

00:24:44.865 --> 00:24:46.585
Then why Bell?

00:24:47.705 --> 00:24:49.065
Why not Champ?

00:24:51.905 --> 00:24:53.585
Jay might know something about this.

00:24:54.625 --> 00:24:56.145
Let's try asking him.

00:24:58.905 --> 00:25:02.025
But before we go home,

00:25:04.625 --> 00:25:06.785
let me do my duty
as a good homeowner first.

00:25:21.585 --> 00:25:24.065
You look more excited
than I am about moving in.

00:25:25.025 --> 00:25:27.425
I'm just doing my job as a good homeowner.

00:25:29.985 --> 00:25:33.025
I wanted black,

00:25:33.545 --> 00:25:35.585
but why did you buy this color for me?

00:25:36.665 --> 00:25:40.785
I think your life needs a bit more color.

00:25:40.865 --> 00:25:43.385
My life isn't dull.

00:25:46.905 --> 00:25:48.225
Where have you guys been?

00:25:48.305 --> 00:25:49.865
I see.

00:25:49.945 --> 00:25:53.345
Hey, Kamin, there's a delivery.
I'll grab it for you.

00:26:01.665 --> 00:26:02.905
Here you are.

00:26:04.585 --> 00:26:05.825
Thank you.

00:26:08.985 --> 00:26:11.105
You even ordered deliveries
to the house now?

00:26:11.185 --> 00:26:12.425
Are you used to it already?

00:26:12.505 --> 00:26:13.745
I guess so.

00:26:21.065 --> 00:26:23.665
Hey, Jay.

00:26:24.865 --> 00:26:26.665
Can I ask you something?

00:26:26.745 --> 00:26:28.065
Sure.

00:26:29.145 --> 00:26:32.905
Did you know Puifai was pregnant?

00:26:33.945 --> 00:26:35.465
Puifai was pregnant?

00:26:37.785 --> 00:26:39.105
You didn't know?

00:26:40.865 --> 00:26:42.105
I didn't.

00:26:44.665 --> 00:26:46.705
You mean she died…

00:26:47.345 --> 00:26:49.105
while she was pregnant?

00:26:49.185 --> 00:26:50.425
No.

00:26:51.865 --> 00:26:54.185
Bell took Puifai to get an abortion.

00:26:59.265 --> 00:27:00.665
You seriously didn't know about this?

00:27:03.065 --> 00:27:04.425
I didn't.

00:27:05.505 --> 00:27:06.665
I only…

00:27:06.745 --> 00:27:10.705
Jay, I get that
you care about your friend,

00:27:10.785 --> 00:27:12.585
but what's done is done.

00:27:13.865 --> 00:27:15.585
There's nothing you can do now.

00:27:16.465 --> 00:27:18.105
Look at me.

00:27:19.985 --> 00:27:21.905
You know something, don't you?

00:27:24.985 --> 00:27:26.385
Look at me!

00:27:30.585 --> 00:27:32.305
Last year, during freshman orientation,

00:27:35.825 --> 00:27:37.545
Puifai and I slept together by accident.

00:27:41.305 --> 00:27:43.145
But it was just a one-night stand.

00:27:43.905 --> 00:27:45.625
Nothing more.

00:27:45.705 --> 00:27:48.265
And you did that
while Champ was dating her, right?

00:27:49.985 --> 00:27:51.465
Are you insane?

00:27:52.225 --> 00:27:54.625
How could you keep
something this big from me?

00:27:54.705 --> 00:27:56.345
I didn't know she was pregnant.

00:27:56.425 --> 00:27:58.225
That baby could've been yours.

00:27:59.185 --> 00:28:02.185
I know what shit
your friends did to Puifai,

00:28:04.345 --> 00:28:07.065
but I pray every day
that you weren't one of them.

00:28:07.145 --> 00:28:09.585
Captain, calm down.

00:28:09.665 --> 00:28:11.265
Don't let emotions take over.

00:28:11.785 --> 00:28:13.785
I tried talking to Puifai.

00:28:16.585 --> 00:28:18.425
She told me to pretend
nothing ever happened.

00:28:18.505 --> 00:28:19.705
I don't believe a word you say anymore.

00:28:19.785 --> 00:28:20.825
Just listen to me first!

00:28:20.905 --> 00:28:22.065
I'm listening!

00:28:22.145 --> 00:28:23.385
I always listen!

00:28:23.465 --> 00:28:25.825
You're the one
who never told me a damn thing!

00:28:25.905 --> 00:28:28.905
- Did you ever try to tell me?
- Don't you wonder why?

00:28:28.985 --> 00:28:31.465
Why we can't talk like we used to?

00:28:33.425 --> 00:28:36.305
Every time I wanted to tell you
or talk about something,

00:28:36.865 --> 00:28:38.425
you never listened properly!

00:28:40.665 --> 00:28:42.465
You've always been like this!

00:29:01.345 --> 00:29:03.065
Are you okay?

00:29:04.585 --> 00:29:06.465
I feel like I don't even know
my own brother.

00:29:10.185 --> 00:29:11.785
Or maybe it's my fault.

00:29:13.225 --> 00:29:15.505
Maybe I made him
too afraid to say anything.

00:30:03.745 --> 00:30:05.025
When did you buy this?

00:30:05.105 --> 00:30:07.705
I don't have just one subordinate,
you know.

00:30:10.585 --> 00:30:11.985
Ken?

00:30:13.345 --> 00:30:15.305
Did you just steal
my favorite subordinate?

00:30:15.905 --> 00:30:17.865
Lieutenant Ken is my subordinate too.

00:30:18.545 --> 00:30:20.865
And he's very dedicated to his work.

00:30:20.945 --> 00:30:23.345
I'm dedicated too.

00:30:25.425 --> 00:30:27.425
Then can I be your favorite subordinate?

00:30:28.225 --> 00:30:29.265
Sure.

00:30:30.905 --> 00:30:31.865
Really?

00:30:31.945 --> 00:30:33.665
Well, if you want to be
just a subordinate,

00:30:34.865 --> 00:30:36.505
then stay just a subordinate.

00:30:40.505 --> 00:30:42.305
Hey, Inspector.

00:30:42.385 --> 00:30:44.985
I didn't know that was even an option.

00:30:49.625 --> 00:30:51.505
You're such a spoiled rich kid.

00:30:51.585 --> 00:30:54.265
I bet you never did this
when you were in the States, right?

00:30:56.585 --> 00:30:58.145
That's right.

00:30:58.225 --> 00:30:59.385
I never did.

00:30:59.985 --> 00:31:02.545
Otherwise, I wouldn't pay
for the expensive hotel

00:31:03.345 --> 00:31:05.185
just to avoid doing stuff like this.

00:31:05.905 --> 00:31:09.145
Well, here I am at your service.

00:31:09.705 --> 00:31:11.345
You won't have to waste money.

00:31:11.985 --> 00:31:15.185
Save it for your love nest.

00:31:16.745 --> 00:31:18.385
And you're going in yourself?

00:31:18.465 --> 00:31:20.145
Not my team.

00:31:20.225 --> 00:31:23.385
The operation is led by Yu
from the Special Investigation Unit.

00:31:24.465 --> 00:31:25.865
Yu?

00:31:28.225 --> 00:31:32.825
Hey, tonight when we hit The Wild Hunt,

00:31:32.905 --> 00:31:37.905
Special Investigation Unit officers Yu
and Lee will be backing us up.

00:31:40.185 --> 00:31:41.625
You got any issues with them?

00:31:42.865 --> 00:31:44.465
Do I need to?

00:31:44.545 --> 00:31:49.225
You looked jumpy
when Jay mentioned that name.

00:31:49.305 --> 00:31:50.745
Why?

00:31:51.945 --> 00:31:53.225
Are you jealous?

00:31:54.505 --> 00:31:58.105
I want to make sure your relationship

00:31:58.185 --> 00:32:00.545
won't interfere with the mission.

00:32:04.665 --> 00:32:08.425
There's nothing going on between us.

00:32:46.985 --> 00:32:49.385
There are CCTV cameras on every pillar.

00:32:50.465 --> 00:32:52.105
Behind the club, there's a curtain.

00:32:53.185 --> 00:32:55.025
It could be a warehouse for drug deals.

00:32:56.665 --> 00:32:58.185
If we get inside,

00:32:58.265 --> 00:33:00.945
we might find clues
about the killer who bought drugs here.

00:33:04.625 --> 00:33:06.785
You got anything today?

00:33:31.585 --> 00:33:33.185
Hands out. Hurry up.

00:33:36.345 --> 00:33:37.225
Shit.

00:33:53.225 --> 00:33:55.345
You came this late.
Did you crawl here or what?

00:33:58.585 --> 00:34:00.105
You're such a pain in the ass.

00:34:00.185 --> 00:34:01.425
- Jade.
- Lee.

00:34:04.385 --> 00:34:06.185
You said there was no problem, right?

00:34:09.824 --> 00:34:11.105
I'm Inspector Kamin.

00:34:11.185 --> 00:34:12.784
This is Captain Jade.

00:34:13.304 --> 00:34:14.545
I think you already know him.

00:34:14.625 --> 00:34:16.865
Yeah. I'm Yu.

00:34:16.945 --> 00:34:17.784
This is Lee.

00:34:18.905 --> 00:34:19.985
We're from the Special Investigation Unit.

00:34:21.225 --> 00:34:22.465
What?

00:34:23.145 --> 00:34:24.105
I don't have any issues.

00:34:24.185 --> 00:34:25.585
You don't have to explain.

00:34:29.824 --> 00:34:32.705
Captain Jade and I
are investigating a drug case.

00:34:33.945 --> 00:34:37.225
Lee and I are investigating
an illegal boxing gambling case.

00:34:37.824 --> 00:34:39.585
If we find anything, we'll let you know.

00:34:43.145 --> 00:34:45.105
If you get any intel,

00:34:46.505 --> 00:34:47.784
feel free to reach out.

00:34:58.185 --> 00:35:00.425
I heard from Nicoli, Kamin's a quiet guy,

00:35:01.105 --> 00:35:02.465
but I didn't expect him to be this quiet.

00:35:03.705 --> 00:35:05.425
And Jade is still a pain
in the ass as always.

00:35:05.505 --> 00:35:06.905
Lee!

00:35:22.265 --> 00:35:23.425
Hello, Inspector.

00:35:24.105 --> 00:35:25.465
My boss is waiting.

00:35:45.705 --> 00:35:47.705
Nice to meet you, Inspector Kananon.

00:35:49.465 --> 00:35:52.625
Or should I just call you Mr. Kamin?

00:35:52.705 --> 00:35:54.745
Let's get straight to the point.

00:36:01.065 --> 00:36:02.505
Ten million

00:36:03.105 --> 00:36:04.505
over two years.

00:36:06.505 --> 00:36:08.625
Would that be enough compensation?

00:36:08.705 --> 00:36:11.385
In exchange for your help with…

00:36:14.225 --> 00:36:16.065
The Wild Hunt.

00:36:21.145 --> 00:36:22.585
Or tell me

00:36:23.785 --> 00:36:25.825
how much you want.

00:36:29.105 --> 00:36:31.305
The only deal I'll make is this.

00:36:33.225 --> 00:36:34.665
Shut this club down.

00:36:38.465 --> 00:36:39.945
Lee Seon Jae.

00:36:40.025 --> 00:36:43.945
I'm arresting you for bribing an officer.

00:36:53.465 --> 00:36:54.945
Hey, I'm heading back.

00:36:59.465 --> 00:37:01.225
Are you really sleeping here tonight?

00:37:01.305 --> 00:37:02.585
Yeah, bro.

00:37:02.665 --> 00:37:04.905
What's with you? You've got a room
and you're still not going back?

00:37:04.985 --> 00:37:06.865
Damn, you're weirdly hardworking.

00:37:06.945 --> 00:37:08.425
Do whatever you want.

00:37:08.505 --> 00:37:09.985
Turn off the lights.

00:37:10.785 --> 00:37:11.745
Got it.

00:37:11.825 --> 00:37:14.745
You don't work during the day
but pull night shifts instead.

00:37:14.825 --> 00:37:16.305
Are you trying to get overtime pay?

00:37:17.465 --> 00:37:19.145
Just go home, bro.

00:37:19.225 --> 00:37:21.585
Stop nagging. I don't want to listen.

00:37:34.945 --> 00:37:36.465
Did you forget something?

00:37:36.545 --> 00:37:37.865
Are you not going home?

00:37:43.985 --> 00:37:45.385
Shit!

00:37:59.825 --> 00:38:01.425
My boss sent me to get you.

00:38:01.505 --> 00:38:03.505
Tell him to show his damn face himself.

00:38:03.585 --> 00:38:06.785
Come quietly, or we'll trade it
for your inspector's corpse.

00:38:14.025 --> 00:38:15.785
Truth or dare, my ass!

00:38:15.865 --> 00:38:17.785
I already chose!

00:38:17.865 --> 00:38:19.625
Bell's fucking dead already!

00:38:19.705 --> 00:38:21.745
Wrong answer.

00:38:27.425 --> 00:38:29.105
Truth.

00:38:29.185 --> 00:38:30.025
Truth.

00:38:30.665 --> 00:38:32.585
It seems like
you've got trouble with your ears.

00:38:33.625 --> 00:38:35.385
Do you understand Thai?

00:38:36.305 --> 00:38:37.945
You're pretty bold.

00:38:38.585 --> 00:38:40.945
Do you want me
to speak your native language?

00:38:49.985 --> 00:38:51.505
Someone like me…

00:38:52.825 --> 00:38:55.225
doesn't like rejection.

00:38:56.065 --> 00:38:57.665
I'm not giving you a choice.

00:38:59.865 --> 00:39:01.465
I'm ordering you as a police officer.

00:39:22.185 --> 00:39:25.185
I'm pretty sure I can pull the trigger
faster than your men.

00:39:27.385 --> 00:39:28.705
Now tell me.

00:39:29.625 --> 00:39:31.065
Who did you sell drugs to?

00:39:33.825 --> 00:39:36.865
A lot of people.

00:39:36.945 --> 00:39:38.345
Don't mess with me!

00:39:40.065 --> 00:39:41.825
The illegal drugs you sold

00:39:42.785 --> 00:39:44.425
are tied to a murder case.

00:39:44.505 --> 00:39:47.265
On top of drug trafficking,

00:39:49.705 --> 00:39:52.025
you'll be charged as an accomplice.

00:39:53.625 --> 00:39:54.825
Really?

00:39:55.945 --> 00:39:57.225
Talk!

00:39:58.785 --> 00:40:00.025
Got it.

00:40:12.865 --> 00:40:15.265
You really want to know, huh?

00:40:16.585 --> 00:40:17.945
All right.

00:40:18.025 --> 00:40:19.585
But first,

00:40:23.185 --> 00:40:26.305
your guy has to win.

00:40:27.065 --> 00:40:30.985
Then I'll tell you.

00:40:38.785 --> 00:40:41.025
And this is a special round.

00:40:41.105 --> 00:40:45.625
Our challenger is the top cop
from the Investigation Unit.

00:40:55.305 --> 00:40:56.985
Is it true

00:40:59.225 --> 00:41:01.265
that money can always buy you?

00:41:02.105 --> 00:41:04.105
No! It's not true!

00:41:04.185 --> 00:41:05.385
It's not!

00:41:05.465 --> 00:41:06.385
No!

00:41:06.465 --> 00:41:08.025
Wasn't it you

00:41:08.105 --> 00:41:11.265
who sold Puifai's clip to Time
in exchange for money?

00:41:12.185 --> 00:41:13.505
Not me!

00:41:14.065 --> 00:41:15.745
I didn't do it!

00:41:15.825 --> 00:41:17.345
I didn't! Not me!

00:41:26.025 --> 00:41:28.025
I sold my friend for money!

00:41:29.345 --> 00:41:31.025
Can you let me go now?

00:41:33.185 --> 00:41:34.745
What the hell do you want from me?

00:41:34.825 --> 00:41:36.345
Your answer is correct.

00:41:38.985 --> 00:41:40.265
Then…

00:41:42.705 --> 00:41:46.265
use that money in hell.

00:41:49.745 --> 00:41:50.945
What the hell are you doing?

00:41:54.985 --> 00:41:57.265
You really care about your guy, huh?

00:41:58.385 --> 00:41:59.705
What should we do?

00:42:05.145 --> 00:42:06.425
Do you want to bet?

00:42:10.505 --> 00:42:12.025
If my guy loses,

00:42:12.865 --> 00:42:14.145
I'll resign.

00:42:15.905 --> 00:42:17.545
But if he wins,

00:42:21.065 --> 00:42:22.745
you're going to prison.

00:42:22.825 --> 00:42:24.905
Nice!

00:42:26.305 --> 00:42:28.945
Go get Hong Wei to handle this cop.

00:42:29.025 --> 00:42:30.585
This is a special match.

00:42:30.665 --> 00:42:34.105
Whoever wins the bet
gets five times the payout.

00:42:42.505 --> 00:42:44.065
This is the only way we survive.

00:42:46.265 --> 00:42:47.905
I've never lost to anyone.

00:42:47.985 --> 00:42:51.345
And the undefeated champion, Hong Wei!

00:42:55.585 --> 00:42:57.185
Even if it's this damn giant.

00:43:00.505 --> 00:43:03.585
Be careful, Jade.

00:43:04.705 --> 00:43:06.465
Inspector,

00:43:06.545 --> 00:43:07.785
if I win,

00:43:08.465 --> 00:43:09.945
can I get…

00:43:11.145 --> 00:43:13.065
what I asked for back at the house?

00:43:13.705 --> 00:43:15.345
Is this really the time to joke around?

00:43:15.425 --> 00:43:17.185
Hey, I'm serious.

00:43:18.305 --> 00:43:19.665
Deal?

00:43:20.745 --> 00:43:21.825
Fine.

00:43:22.345 --> 00:43:23.825
Just don't lose.

00:43:54.345 --> 00:43:56.385
Don't waste your time being jealous of me.

00:43:57.425 --> 00:44:00.185
I've never helped Yu make a bed like this.

00:44:01.105 --> 00:44:03.345
You're my first, Inspector.

00:44:04.465 --> 00:44:05.865
Ever.

00:44:18.185 --> 00:44:21.105
I don't have eyes for anyone but you.

00:44:22.505 --> 00:44:25.025
Honestly, we don't have
to go through all this.

00:44:25.105 --> 00:44:27.105
Just move into my room.

00:44:27.185 --> 00:44:28.705
It's way easier.

00:44:28.785 --> 00:44:30.905
I signed a lease agreement,

00:44:32.145 --> 00:44:34.145
not a "sleep-in-the-same-room"
contract with you.

00:44:34.225 --> 00:44:39.865
Well then, I'll upgrade the lease
to a VVIP contract.

00:44:46.225 --> 00:44:47.745
I'll give you one night to think about it.

00:44:49.145 --> 00:44:50.745
I'll come get your answer.

00:44:53.745 --> 00:44:56.825
Right now, it feels like the culprit
is always one step ahead of us.

00:44:58.465 --> 00:45:00.345
They know everything we're about to do.

00:45:00.425 --> 00:45:03.025
That's why I suspect the culprit
might be someone on the inside.

00:45:03.105 --> 00:45:04.945
You guys seem pretty close.

00:45:05.025 --> 00:45:07.025
I was wondering if you ever…

00:45:08.345 --> 00:45:09.505
You mean, were we dating?

00:45:09.585 --> 00:45:12.745
Are we more than just boss
and subordinate now?

00:45:12.825 --> 00:45:15.345
It's been that way for a long time.
You're the only one who didn't notice.